{%- block heading %}
## SECTION {{ slNum }} (Maximum Marks: {{ maxMarks }}){.text-center}
{%- endblock %}

{%- block sectioninfo %}
- This section contains **{{ totalQuestions | toWords | upcase }} ({{ totalQuestions | zeroPad: 2 }})** questions.
{%- endblock %}
{%- block questioninfo %}
- Each question contains two columns, **Column-I** and **Column-II**.
- **Column-I** has **{{ answerOptions.rows.count | toWords | upcase }}** entries {{ answerOptions.rows.chars | joinInEnglish: '(', ')' }}.
- **Column-II** has **{{ answerOptions.cols.count | toWords | upcase }}** entries {{ answerOptions.cols.chars | joinInEnglish: '(', ')' }}.
- Match the entries in **Column-I** with the entries in **Column-II**.
- One or more entries in **Column-I** may match with one or more entries in **Column-II**.
{%- endblock %}
{%- block eachquestion %}
- For each entry in **Column-I**, select the options of all the matching entries. For example, if entry ({{ answerOptions.rows.chars[0] }}) in **Column-I** matches with entries {{ answerOptions.cols.chars | slice: 0, 3 | joinInEnglish: '(', ')' }}, then choose these {{ answerOptions.cols.chars | slice: 0, 3 | size | toWords | downcase }} options. Similarly, for entries {{ answerOptions.rows.chars | slice: 1, answerOptions.rows.count | joinInEnglish: '(', ')' }}.
{%- endblock %}
{%- block markingscheme %}
- Answers to each question will be evaluated _according to the following marking scheme_:
  - For each entry in **Column-I**
  - |-----------------|---|-------------|
    | *Full Marks*    |&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;| {{ questionMarks.correct | prepend: "+" }} if **ONLY** the option(s) corresponding to all the correct options(s) is(are) chosen; |
    {%- if questionMarks.incorrect == 0 %}
    | *Zero Marks*    |&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;| 0 In all other cases. |
    {%- else %}
    | *Zero Marks*    |&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;| 0 If none of the options is chosen (i.e., the question is unanswered); |
    | *Negative Marks* {.text-nowrap}|&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;| {{ questionMarks.incorrect }} In all other cases. |
    {%- endif %}
    {.no-border}
{%- endblock %}
